Mbps 以上），要有独立 IP （至少一个），接受共享带宽；\r\n\r\n2. 便宜；\r\n\r\n3. 主机本身**不需要**太高性能，不限 x86/arm ，大概树莓派的水平能跑 Linux 就行；\r\n\r\n4. 无所谓主机在国内的哪；\r\n\r\n有无好推荐？", "content_rendered": "<p>主要需求：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>带宽高（ 50Mbps 以上），要有独立 IP （至少一个），接受共享带宽；</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>便宜；</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>主机本身<strong>不需要</strong>太高性能，不限 x86/arm ，大概树莓派的水平能跑 Linux 就行；</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>无所谓主机在国内的哪；</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p>有无好推荐？</p>\n", "last_modified": 1653899039, "replies": 54, "id": 856248}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1650095340", "name": "qna", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1650095340", "title": "问与答", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna", "topics": 185426, "footer": "", "header": "一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。", "title_alternative": "Questions and Answers", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340", "stars": 3485, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 12, "parent_node_name": "v2ex"}, "member": {"id": 467934, "username": "yuhangch", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/yuhangch", "website": "https://yuhang.ch", "twitter": "yuhangch", "psn": "", "github": "yuhangch", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/0cc7/3790/467934_mini.png?m=1651720222", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/0cc7/3790/467934_normal.png?m=1651720222", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/0cc7/3790/467934_large.png?m=1651720222", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/0cc7/3790/467934_xlarge.png?m=1651720222", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/0cc7/3790/467934_xlarge.png?m=1651720222", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/0cc7/3790/467934_xlarge.png?m=1651720222", "created": 1580887263, "last_modified": 1651720222}, "last_reply_by": "hzlzh", "last_touched": 1653984362, "title": "各位推荐些播客吧", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/856357", "created": 1653959663, "deleted": 0, "content": "平台没关系，科技、资讯等等", "content_